3	// compare_adapter.go provides comparison, quorum, and benchmark execution
4	// helpers for DDx. The compare/quorum/benchmark execution logic accepts a
5	// run-function closure so production callers can drive arms via the agent
6	// service (RunViaService) while legacy Runner-bound tests can keep using
7	// Runner.Run.
